<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head lang="en">
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Absolute center align</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; }

        body {
            background: green;
        }

        #container {
            width: 500px; height: 250px;
            background: orange;

            /* 위치 설정 */
            position: absolute;
            left: 50%; top: 50%;
            margin-left: -250px;
            margin-top: -125px;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="container">
        <h1>절대 좌표를 사용한 중앙 정렬</h1>
    </div>
</body>
</html>